<assessmentItem xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqti_v2p1 http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/qti/qtiv2p1/imsqti_v2p1p1.xsd http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML http://www.w3.org/Math/XMLSchema/mathml2/mathml2.xsd" identifier="id052218b9-c073-4f15-928d-7ab6a7a07905" title="DetBerechnungsFormeln" adaptive="false" timeDependent="false"><responseDeclaration identifier="RESPONSE_1" cardinality="multiple" baseType="identifier"><correctResponse><value>id18d42978-73fb-439a-8e69-113fccee181b</value><value>ide8dfdf05-4efa-4b1f-9533-55ff1de72144</value><value>idcf06ba98-9abe-4a2a-afa7-4e85b5b6c38d</value><value>id400fd96b-cd92-4e45-8952-aeac8da17729</value></correctResponse></responseDeclaration><outcomeDeclaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" baseType="float"><defaultValue><value>0</value></defaultValue></outcomeDeclaration><outcomeDeclaration identifier="MAXSCORE" cardinality="single" baseType="float"><defaultValue><value>9</value></defaultValue></outcomeDeclaration><outcomeDeclaration identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC" cardinality="single" baseType="identifier"><defaultValue><value>empty</value></defaultValue></outcomeDeclaration><itemBody ><p>Sei</p><p>$$M =\left( \begin{array}{ccccc} a_{11} &amp; \cdots &amp; a_{1j} &amp; \cdots &amp;a_{1n} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots &amp; &amp;  \vdots \\a_{i1} &amp; \cdots &amp; a_{ij} &amp; \cdots &amp; a_{in} \\ \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots &amp; &amp; \vdots \\ a_{n1} &amp; \cdots &amp; a_{nj} &amp; \cdots &amp; a_{nn} \end{array}\right)$$  eine nxn Matrix.</p><p>Sei <strong>\(M_{ij}\)</strong> die Matrix die entsteht wenn man in <strong>M die i 'te Zeile</strong> und <strong>j'te Spalte</strong> streicht.</p><p>Wähle aus, durch welche Formeln die Determinante von M ausgerechnet werden kann:</p><p> </p><choiceInteraction responseIdentifier="RESPONSE_1" shuffle="true" maxChoices="0"><simpleChoice identifier="id18d42978-73fb-439a-8e69-113fccee181b"><p> </p><p>$$Für \ 1 \leq j \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{k=1}^{n}(-1)^{k+j} \cdot a_{kj} \cdot det(M_{kj}) = \sum_{k=1}^{n}(-1)^{k+j}  \cdot a_{jk} \cdot det(M_{jk})$$</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="ide8dfdf05-4efa-4b1f-9533-55ff1de72144"><p> </p><p>$$Für \ n = 3 \ und \ 1 \leq j \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{k=1}^{3}(-1)^{k+j} \cdot a_{jk} \cdot det(M_{jk})  =  a_{11} \cdot a_{22} \cdot a_{33} + a_{12} \cdot a_{23} \cdot a_{31} + a_{13} \cdot a_{21} \cdot a_{32} - a_{31} \cdot a_{22} \cdot a_{13}- a_{32} \cdot a_{23} \cdot a_{11}- a_{33} \cdot a_{21} \cdot a_{12}$$</p><p> </p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="id3305e322-f22f-4d0a-aa02-545aa9259abd"><p> </p><p>$$Für \ 1 \leq i \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{j=1}^{i}(-1)^{i+j} \cdot a_{jn} \cdot det(M_{jn}) $$</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="idad870882-cab0-4adb-bfb0-c3306bd2bf4b"><p> </p><p>$$Für \ 1 \leq i \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{j=1}^{n}(-1)^{i+j} \cdot a_{jn} \cdot det(M_{jn}) $$</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="id1e2b7c57-0178-4566-92dc-112638b9a1c7"><p> </p><p>$$Für \ 1 \leq j \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{k=1}^{n} - 1^{k+j} \cdot a_{kj} \cdot det(M_{kj}) $$</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="idcf06ba98-9abe-4a2a-afa7-4e85b5b6c38d"><p> </p><p> $$ Für \ 3  \leq n : \ Det (M) = \sum_{j=1}^{n}(-1)^{3+j} \cdot a_{j3} \cdot det(M_{j3}) $$</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="id400fd96b-cd92-4e45-8952-aeac8da17729"><p> </p><p>$$ Für \ 4 \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{j=1}^{n}(-1)^{j} \cdot a_{j2} \cdot det(M_{j2}) $$</p></simpleChoice><simpleChoice identifier="ide26be9d2-e002-4d6e-85a7-2b0894373f39"><p> </p><p>$$ Für \ 4 \leq n: \ Det (M) = \sum_{i=1}^{n}(-1)^{n+i} \cdot a_{3i} \cdot det(M_{3i}) $$</p></simpleChoice></choiceInteraction></itemBody><responseProcessing><responseCondition><responseIf><isNull><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></isNull><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">empty</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseIf><responseElseIf><match><variable identifier="RESPONSE_1" /><correct identifier="RESPONSE_1" /></match><setOutcomeValue identifier="SCORE"><sum><variable identifier="SCORE" /><variable identifier="MAXSCORE" /></sum></setOutcomeValue><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">correct</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseElseIf><responseElse><setOutcomeValue identifier="FEEDBACKBASIC"><baseValue baseType="identifier">incorrect</baseValue></setOutcomeValue></responseElse></responseCondition></responseProcessing></assessmentItem>
